OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FA new board is being created to
OL,8,Foversee improvements at the Nottingham
OL,9,FNHS trust at the centre of the
OL,10,Fcountry's maternity scandal.
OL,12,FIt follows publication of the Ockenden
OL,13,Freport, led by senior midwife Donna
OL,14,FOckenden, which investigated serious
OL,15,Ffailings in maternity services at the
OL,16,FQueen's Medical Centre and Nottingham
OL,17,FCity Hospital.
OL,19,FThey are both run by the Nottingham
OL,20,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe report found 520 mothers and
OL,8,Fbabies suffered harm or died when it
OL,9,Fcould have been prevented, and that
OL,10,Fsenior leaders failed to take action
OL,12,FThe board will provide independent
OL,13,Fchecks on the delivery of
OL,14,Fimprovements, with a particular focus
OL,15,Fon 'safety, quality and learning'
OL,16,Facross maternity services.
OL,18,FIt will be chaired by Sherwood MP,
OL,19,FMichelle Welsh, who has previously
OL,20,Fcampaigned for improvements to
OL,21,Fmaternity services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FMs Welsh said: "The findings of the
OL,8,FIndependent Maternity Review reinforce
OL,9,Fthe urgent need for change in our
OL,10,Fmaternity services. For that reason, I
OL,11,Fhave agreed to Chair the NUH Learning
OL,12,Fand Improvement Board.
OL,14,F"I acknowledge the suffering
OL,15,Fexperienced by the families at the
OL,16,Fheart of this review, whose courage in
OL,17,Fspeaking out has brought to light the
OL,18,Fdesperate need for change.
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"Having campaigned for improvements in
OL,8,Fmaternity services for the past five
OL,9,Fand a half years, I am committed to
OL,10,Fworking collectively with families,
OL,11,Fstaff and partners to ensure lasting
OL,12,Fimprovements are made."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
