OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FAnthony May, Chief Executive of NUH,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The publication of the
OL,9,FIndependent Maternity Review is a
OL,10,Fwatershed moment, particularly for the
OL,11,Faffected women and families who have
OL,12,Fengaged with the Review. It is very
OL,13,Fimportant that we have robust,
OL,14,Findependent oversight of the
OL,15,Fimplementation of the Review's
OL,16,Ffindings. We are committed to a
OL,17,Fcomprehensive and sustained response
OL,18,Fto every action.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"Two years ago, we made a public
OL,8,Fcommitment to ensure continued
OL,9,Fscrutiny of our maternity services,
OL,10,Fand this Board is a key part of
OL,11,Fdelivering on that promise.
OL,13,F"In the coming weeks, we will publish
OL,14,Fa detailed action plan setting out how
OL,15,Fevery action will be addressed, with
OL,16,Fclear timescales and named
OL,17,Faccountability. We will continue to
OL,18,Finvolve families and staff in shaping
OL,19,Four response, and in holding us to
OL,20,Faccount.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
