PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782461893
OL,3,CBoard created to oversee improvements
OL,4,Cat NHS trust at heart of maternity
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"We will work closely with the
OL,8,FLearning and Improvement Board, NHS
OL,9,FEngland, our regulators,
OL,10,Fcommissioners, local families,
OL,11,Fpartners and maternity experts to
OL,12,Fensure improvements are delivered and
OL,13,Fsustained."
OL,15,FSupport and advice available for
OL,16,Fparents and families:
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@KO]
